{"tid":1040303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"猥褻兒女遭揭發　鬼父懷恨！竟恐嚇「強姦社工」","createTime":"2019-02-28T04:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T07:11:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"871418fec4a706caab89ca6074486aa92394851d","tid":1040303,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:03:01.000Z","msg":"猥褻未成年兒女，甚至還恐嚇「強姦社工」，桃園鬼父言行超誇張！<br />\n《聯合報》報導，桃園陳姓男子，2005年起5次吸未成年女兒、有中度智能障礙兒子的乳頭被社工揭發，被依妨害性自主等判刑4年，一直到去年5月才執行完畢。<br />\n出獄後的陳男對社工懷恨在心，去年9月到11月期間，多次打電話到家防中心騷擾社工，不但辱罵三字經，還恐嚇說「我要帶刀子去，不滿意就故意捅，看我敢不敢」、「(社工)來我家要強姦她嗎？」，誇張言行讓家防中心提出告訴。<br />\n陳男到案時坦承犯行，遭檢方依恐嚇罪嫌起訴。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190228/640_599c97c68cf8e06211f8bab88bdbece5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190228%2F640_599c97c68cf8e06211f8bab88bdbece5.jpg&h=c9184f7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03e3444706ceb09e4eb41bceb1706501fd40a14a","tid":1040303,"uid":18569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:05:33.000Z","msg":"又入波啦<br />\n今日已經入左唔知幾多球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7cfa81f90e39b464529336be05a14367231fd03","tid":1040303,"uid":48917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:07:03.000Z","msg":"好似之前一套漫畫日記的劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8cb27f1c425804602182589bf86dc1b6ee7a76","tid":1040303,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:10:43.000Z","msg":"舊式鍵盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55cea8a522ba966b7bd0d804b41546bb948775e1","tid":1040303,"uid":1067,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:11:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/24330\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F24330&d=HVFDXqn9k